rows.label: qst102908_msg001
rows.name:
Somewhere in the old city,
there's a memo with three
hints hidden. Go find it.

rows.label: qst102908_msg002
rows.name:
When you find it, I'll give
you half of what's inside,
so come report to me.

rows.label: qst102908_msg101
rows.name:
The memo is in three places
somewhere in the old city.
